lumn][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1440811735826{margin-bottom: 0px !important;border-bottom-width: 0px !important;}\"]\n<h1 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">INNOVATION SPOTLIGHT</h1>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1441049736683{margin-top: -30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/12\"][vc_separator color=\"custom\" border_width=\"3\" el_width=\"60\" accent_color=\"#7bc142\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_raw_html]\n\\n\n[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442346443279{margin-top: 0px !important;border-top-width: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"]Inventor Michael Manion chats about his long-standing working relationship with IDF – how it has helped him generate new solutions for specific challenges, and how it has enabled him to fulfill his childhood dream of becoming an inventor.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_raw_html]\n\\n\n[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442346470053{margin-top: 0px !important;border-top-width: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"]Entrepreneur Jose Torres is taking his invention to market in a collaborative engagement with IDF that includes business development and marketing assistance through our Sponsored Invention services..\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_type=\"image\" bg_image_pos=\"cover\" padding_top=\"140\" padding_bottom=\"140\" font_color=\"#212121\" css=\".vc_custom_1441058056647{padding-top: 70px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-image: url(http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Home-About-Background4.jpg) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\" el_id=\"about\" bg_image=\"2967\"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1441042704994{margin-bottom: 0px !important;border-bottom-width: 0px !important;}\"]\n<h1 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ABOUT US</h1>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1441049736683{margin-top: -30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/12\"][vc_separator color=\"custom\" border_width=\"3\" el_width=\"60\" accent_color=\"#7bc142\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442344767474{margin-top: 0px !important;border-top-width: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"]The Invention Development Fund was established in 2007 as a new part of the Intellectual Ventures family of Investment Funds focused on building a global inventor network. IDF invents on behalf of its many customers in a variety of industries, ranging from huge multinational food and beverage or credit card companies to startups and regional Small &amp; Medium Enterprises (SMEs).\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442622625312{margin-top: 0px !important;border-top-width: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"]IDF cultivates working relationships with inventors worldwide through its 10,000-strong global invention network, representing more than 400 research institutions and universities.\n\nIntellectual Ventures helps create a world in which invention can thrive through the shared commitment to research, collaboration, investment, and defense of inventors’ rights.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"OUR TEAM\" style=\"outline\" color=\"custom\" size=\"xlg\" align=\"right\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fabout%2F||\" custom_color=\"#0e73a3\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1 class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" style=\"outline\" color=\"white\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}s:21:\"footer-cta_1975823092\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:10:\"Footer CTA\";s:8:\"template\";s:762:\"[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}s:19:\"services_1983621855\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"Services\";s:8:\"template\";s:6435:\"[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_type=\"image\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h2>OVERVIEW</h2>\nIDF provides a full suite of consulting and innovation services, capabilities, and global connectivity. These services can be tailored to meet your needs, or provided through an integrated <strong>Sponsored Invention</strong> engagement.\n\nFrom initial collaboration, defining challenges and industry opportunities, to our solution innovation and business development support, IDF will work as your innovation partner, fully invested in mutual success.[/vc_column_text][vc_tta_tour][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-lightbulb-o\" title=\"Opportunities &amp; Strategy\" tab_id=\"1441142697616-9772428f-dd1c\" add_icon=\"true\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442865250526{padding-left: 30px !important;}\"]\n\nIDF’s invention experts will partner with your company’s thought leaders, technologists, and stakeholders to identify your key business and technology challenges. We translate these challenges into innovation opportunities as we work in collaboration to clearly understand the technical landscape, existing solution gaps, and technical needs required for success.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_type=\"linecons\" i_icon_linecons=\"vc_li vc_li-megaphone\" title=\"Co-Invention Session\" tab_id=\"1441142938988-df4098ea-edf7\" add_icon=\"true\"][vc_column_text]\n\nAn IDF <em>Co-Invention Session</em> is the ultimate think tank event – focused entirely on meeting your company’s specific challenges. Based on the technical challenges identified in our initial discussions, we assemble our best experts and spend the day in purposeful creative dialog, capturing all emerging ideas for subsequent evaluation and consideration toward real-world solutions.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_type=\"linecons\" i_icon_linecons=\"vc_li vc_li-settings\" title=\"IP-Minded Consulting\" tab_id=\"1441142697870-b0d00517-aa87\" add_icon=\"true\"][vc_column_text]\n\nWe carefully consider industry trends, technology insights, competitive landscapes, and IP strategy to assist you in creating a roadmap to success. Our highly experienced team will help you evaluate emerging opportunities and design a technology pathway to take advantage of new innovations.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-users\" title=\"Invention Network Solutions\" tab_id=\"1441142981313-aaf03c6e-3a4b\" add_icon=\"true\"][vc_column_text]The Intellectual Ventures Inventor Network (IVIN) consists of more than 10,000 individual inventors and 400 institutions located all around the world. Unlike the typical “crowd-source” invention approach, IDF has well-established working relationships with all of the IVIN members. According to the specific invention need, we call upon the most suitable skillsets to help us seek solutions.\n\nIVIN inventors can be significant participants in Inventor Brainstorm Sessions and responders to our Request For Invention (RFI) process.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-child\" title=\"Request for Invention\" tab_id=\"1441142982681-a311e3b4-3c34\" add_icon=\"true\"][vc_column_text]\n\nTo solicit new ideas from our global inventor network, we send out a Request for Invention (RFI). This unique document clearly defines the specific technical challenge to be solved on behalf of your organization. The content of the RFI is carefully crafted to elicit inventive concepts and to obtain optimal technical solutions on your behalf.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_type=\"openiconic\" i_icon_openiconic=\"vc-oi vc-oi-chart-pie\" title=\"Patent Portfolio Access\" tab_id=\"1441142984157-e3537e79-ac88\" add_icon=\"true\"][vc_column_text]Fortify your IP position through licensing or acquiring additional assets from IDF’s diverse collection of patents. We have a unique set of patents and invention assets that can complement your existing set of patented innovations.\n\n<a href=\"http://inventiondevfund.com/patent-search/\">VIEW PATENTS</a> &gt;[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-globe\" title=\"Global Market Relationships\" tab_id=\"1441142986472-dc3d765b-f9b1\" add_icon=\"true\"][vc_column_text]IDF has highly valuable connections in rapidly emerging industries and global markets. Our international relationships can help to accelerate your entry into new markets around the world.\n\n<a href=\"http://inventiondevfund.com/portfolio-item/coffee-flour/\">READ OUR CASE STUDY</a> &gt;[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-rocket\" title=\"Sponsored Invention Engagement \" tab_id=\"1442865963750-f8fc0894-6c18\" add_icon=\"true\"][vc_raw_html]\n\\n\n[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text]<em>Sponsored Invention - powerful innovation services delivering highly focused solutions</em>\n\nTake a look inside our Sponsored Invention solution in the context of just one of the dozens of industries in which we operate. To learn more about how we can support your specific needs, <a href=\"/contact-us/\">let’s talk.</a>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tour][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}s:21:\"contact-us_1139748021\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:10:\"Contact Us\";s:8:\"template\";s:400:\"[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><em>\"Our partnership with IDF is providing the necessary elements to position us for ongoing success on a global scale.\"</em></h3>\n— Dan Belliveau, Coffee Flour CEO\n<h3>OUR HEADQUARTERS</h3>\n3150 139th Ave SE, Building 4 | Bellevue, WA 98005[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][gravityform id=\"1\" ajax=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}s:20:\"home-11-24_264781790\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:10:\"Home 11-24\";s:8:\"template\";s:15519:\"[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\"][vc_column offset=\"vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm\"][vc_single_image image=\"3045\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1440808207034{margin-top: 80px !important;margin-bottom: 90px !important;}\" padding_top=\"20\" padding_bottom=\"20\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1441264818834{padding-bottom: -40px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_separator color=\"custom\" align=\"align_left\" border_width=\"3\" el_width=\"50\" accent_color=\"#7bc142\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">MULTI-NATIONAL SEEKING INNOVATION</h4>\n<em>\"This collaboration [with IDF] aims to enhance the innovation pipelines available to AkzoNobel to help us achieve our goal of continued improvement and new product introductions.\"</em>\n\n<span style=\"color: #858c8c;\">— Jos Keurentjes<em> </em></span>\n<span style=\"color: #858c8c;\">Director of Open Innovation</span>\n<span style=\"color: #858c8c;\"><a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/portfolio-item/case-study-akzonobel/\">AkzoNobel</a></span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1441264818834{padding-bottom: -40px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_separator color=\"custom\" align=\"align_left\" border_width=\"3\" el_width=\"50\" accent_color=\"#7bc142\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">MID-SIZE COMPANY POISED FOR GROWTH</h4>\n<em>\"The ability to scale and grow this business was always something in the back of our minds. But we knew we didn’t have the expertise or the resources, and that’s what IDF brings to the party.\"</em>\n\n<span style=\"color: #858c8c;\">— Rick Osterhout<em> </em></span>\n<span style=\"color: #858c8c;\">Executive Vice President</span>\n<span style=\"color: #858c8c;\"><a href=\"/portfolio-item/collinswoerman/\">Collins Woerman</a></span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1441264818834{padding-bottom: -40px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_separator color=\"custom\" align=\"align_left\" border_width=\"3\" el_width=\"50\" accent_color=\"#7bc142\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">INNOVATOR NEEDS BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT</h4>\n<em>“Working with IDF – engineers, business development experts, and IP strategists – we now have the resources and expertise to accelerate partnerships with developers and innovators.”</em>\n\n<span style=\"color: #858c8c;\">— Jose Torres<em> </em></span>\n<span style=\"color: #858c8c;\">CEO</span>\n<span style=\"color: #858c8c;\"><a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/portfolio-item/reflx-labs-boogio/\">REFLX Labs</a></span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" padding_bottom=\"50px\" css_animation_delay=\"10\" css=\".vc_custom_1440