>\n<h1><span style=\"color: #194265;\"><strong>NEW</strong> TECHNOLOGY IS NEEDED</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1449788837290{padding-left: 25px !important;}\"]\n<ul>\n	<li class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">Consumer Emotional Anticipation Analysis</h4>\n</li>\n	<li class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">Improved Models for Reaction Analysis</h4>\n</li>\n	<li class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Flawless Interpretation of Micro-Expression Data</h4>\n</li>\n	<li class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Automate Systems for Facial Recognition</h4>\n</li>\n	<li class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">Refinement and Automation of FACS</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3181\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"0\" padding_bottom=\"40\" font_color=\"#4d4d4d\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042963431{background-color: #f6f6f6 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_moving_box content_type=\"icon\" icon_type=\"typicons\" icon_size=\"54px\" icon_typicons=\"typcn typcn-arrow-down\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" css_animation_delay=\"200\" css=\".vc_custom_1449100474973{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 70px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 52px; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"color: #194265;\">WHY</span> <strong><span style=\"color: #ff940e;\">INVENT WITH US?</span></strong></h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"We Promote Innovation Through A Global Community of Inventors\" color=\"custom\" border_width=\"2\" el_width=\"50\" accent_color=\"#194265\" el_class=\"reduce-margin-top\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" css=\".vc_custom_1449023373109{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"3114\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\"><span style=\"color: #194265;\">Global Community</span></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Collaborate with an international community of inventors</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Have your inventions evaluated and potentially licensed</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Explore new realms for invention with industry defined problems to be solved</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"3116\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\"><span style=\"color: #194265;\">Financial Reward</span></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Receive upfront payments and patenting for selected inventions</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Share in profits and royalties from licensing and commercialization</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Gain opportunities for technical development funding</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"3127\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\"><span style=\"color: #194265;\">Focus on Inventing</span></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Ability to concentrate on research, development and the invention process</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Receive help securing patents and commercially promoting your inventions</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Gain international exposure through our established networks</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Bill-Walsh.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-3128 aligncenter\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Bill-Walsh.png\" alt=\"Bill-Walsh\" width=\"250\" height=\"248\" /></a></p>\n\n<em>\"Working with the Invention Development Fund (IDF), is like working with a personal trainer. IDF provides the motivation as well as intellectual environment to get the best of our team. They have challenged us to provide the solutions and supported these ideas through a thorough understanding of the intellectual property landscape.”</em>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">_</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Professor Bill Walsh</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Inventor and Lead Researcher</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">University of New South Wales</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Sydney, Australia</div>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Shmuel-Ur.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3130\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Shmuel-Ur.png\" alt=\"Shmuel-Ur\" width=\"250\" height=\"248\" /></a></p>\n\n<em>\"Professional isolation is not good for the inventor’s soul. I find collaborating with other IVIN members often leads to better ideas, in fact, some of my recruits have become co-authors on inventions I\'ve subsequently sold to Intellectual Ventures. For me, getting to focus on idea generation and leave the IP protection to someone else is a great opportunity to invent in realms I could not access otherwise. I credit more than half of my income and much of my success to Intellectual Ventures. There’s no other company besides IV that buys ideas from independent innovators.\"</em>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">_</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Dr. Shmuel Ur</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Full-time Inventor and</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">CEO of Shmuel Ur Inovations Ltd.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Shorashim, Israel</div>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Mike-Manion.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-3129 aligncenter\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Mike-Manion.png\" alt=\"Mike-Manion\" width=\"250\" height=\"248\" /></a></p>\n\n<em>\"I started inventing with IVIDF about 5 years ago and it\'s allowed me to build my company. I started inventing alone on nights and weekends, but now, because of the work we do with IDF, it\'s allowed me to hire inventors, train people on inventing and build a lab where we can basically prototype anything we want to. IDF has enabled me to become a full time inventor. It\'s really a boyhood dream come true.\"</em>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">_</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Dr. Michael Manion</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Full-time Inventor and</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">CEO of Keon Research</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Seattle, USA</div>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1449608302737{margin-bottom: -50px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_moving_box content_type=\"icon\" icon_type=\"typicons\" icon_size=\"54px\" icon_typicons=\"typcn typcn-arrow-down\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" padding_top=\"-10\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_bottom=\"-10\" bg_color=\"#194265\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" delimiter=\"vline\" css=\".vc_custom_1449953324432{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1449616747342{margin-left: 10px !important;}\"]\n<h1 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\">GET STARTED TODAY!</h1>\n<h3 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Join IVIN today to receive further information on this invention opportunity, or to submit your invention for consideration.</h3>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"SIGN UP NOW!\" color=\"custom\" size=\"xlg\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:https%3A%2F%2Fivin.intven.com%2Fsignup|title:IVIN%20Sign%20Up|target:%20_blank\" custom_color=\"#ff940e\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1449953371424{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #658dc6 !important;}\" el_class=\"question-form\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1 class=\"p1\">HAVE A QUESTION?</h1>\n[/vc_column_text][gravityform id=\"3\" ajax=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_type=\"image\" bg_image_pos=\"cover\" padding_top=\"140\" padding_bottom=\"140\" font_color=\"#212121\" css=\".vc_custom_1441058056647{padding-top: 70px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-image: url(http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Home-About-Background4.jpg) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\" bg_image=\"2967\"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1449090389402{margin-bottom: 0px !important;border-bottom-width: 0px !important;}\" el_class=\"about_us\"]\n<h1 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ABOUT US</h1>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1441049736683{margin-top: -30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/12\"][vc_separator color=\"custom\" border_width=\"3\" el_width=\"60\" accent_color=\"#7bc142\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1450118699238{margin-top: 0px !important;border-top-width: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"]\n<p class=\"p2\">The Invention Development Fund was established in 2007 as a new part of the Intellectual Ventures family of Investment Funds focused on building a global inventor network. IDF invents on behalf of its many customers in a variety of industries, ranging from huge multinational food and beverage or credit card companies to startups and regional Small &amp; Medium Enterprises (SMEs). IDF cultivates working relationships with inventors worldwide through its 10,000-strong global invention network (IVIN).</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1449090664800{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"JOIN OUR INVENTOR COMMUNITY\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" link=\"url:https%3A%2F%2Fivin.intven.com%2Fsignup||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}}','no'),(790,'portfolio-type_children','a:0:{}','yes'),(977,'bvSecretKey','3fbe1cc1a25ed9540985c8a0dca2e961','yes'),(978,'bvActivateRed