=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442846061770{margin-top: 0px !important;border-top-width: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"]\r\n\r\nThe Invention Development Fund was established in 2007 as a new part of the Intellectual Ventures family of Investment Funds focused on building a global inventor network. IDF invents on behalf of its many customers in a variety of industries, ranging from huge multinational food and beverage or credit card companies to startups and regional Small &amp; Medium Enterprises (SMEs).\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1444924330322{margin-top: 0px !important;border-top-width: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"]IDF cultivates working relationships with inventors worldwide through its 10,000-strong global invention network, representing more than 400 research institutions and universities.\r\n\r\nIntellectual Ventures helps create a world in which invention can thrive through the shared commitment to research, collaboration, investment, and inventors’ rights.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"MEET OUR TEAM\" color=\"om-theme-color\" hover_color=\"custom\" text_color=\"custom\" size=\"xlg\" align=\"right\" link=\"url:https%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fabout%2F||\" hover_custom_color=\"#707ca3\" text_custom_color=\"#ffffff\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:https%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Homepage','','publish','open','open','','homepage','','','2016-03-11 22:17:44','2016-03-11 22:17:44','',0,'http://demo.olevmedia.net/amax/?page_id=85',0,'page','',0),(99,1,'2014-12-03 09:48:00','2014-12-03 09:48:00','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">INNOVATION BRINGS NEW FOOD SOURCE TO LIFE</h2>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Transformative process provides nutritional, economic, and environmental benefits worldwide. The team behind Coffee Flour™ saw a long-standing problem in need of a solution and invented a process for turning the unvalued coffee cherry pulp cast off in the harvest of coffee beans into nutritious and tasty flour.</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>FRUITFUL OPPORTUNITY</h2>\nIn traditional processing, coffee beans are separated from coffee cherries, and the remaining fruit pulp is discarded. Every year, more than a billion pounds of this unused by- product is left to decompose, often causing unintended harm to local ecosystems. Seeking a solution to this ongoing problem, inventor Dan Belliveau began to develop a process that would convert the coffee cherry pulp into a new, all-natural food ingredient now known as Coffee Flour.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=9&amp;v=wKPUskVtGow\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2572\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441134053801{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442858480635{margin-right: 10px !important;}\"]\n<h2>COLLABORATIVE DEVELOPMENT</h2>\nBelliveau sought out partners who could help translate his early successes into a product for the global marketplace. He engaged the support of Intellectual Ventures who assisted with funding and legal issues, as well as practical product development activities, including nutritional analysis, ingredient testing, certifications, and test kitchen work. Collaboration led to the involvement of several key players in the food process supply chain, including distributors and grower-producer companies around the globe.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>SHARED BENEFITS</h2>\nNow carried forward by a newly formed company, CF Global Holdings Inc., the Coffee Flour innovation will provide fresh culinary possibilities to kitchens worldwide with a healthy, flavorful new food ingredient. This ecologically smart use of a formerly discarded byproduct not only adds to the food supply, but also offers improved income stability for small coffee farmers and their local economies.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2570\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1451961151592{margin-right: 35px !important;}\"]\n<h2></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">“<em>Our partnership with IDF is providing the necessary elements to position us for ongoing success on a global scale.</em>”</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">— Dan Belliveau, CF Global Holdings Founder and CEO</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Coffee Flour','','publish','closed','closed','','coffee-flour','','','2016-01-05 02:32:19','2016-01-05 02:32:19','',0,'http://demo.olevmedia.net/amax/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=99',2,'portfolio','',0),(189,1,'2015-03-23 13:00:14','2015-03-23 13:00:14','','ANIEL VERONICO','','publish','closed','closed','','aniel-veronico','','','2015-03-23 13:00:14','2015-03-23 13:00:14','',0,'http://newthemes.themeple.co/vision_wp/?post_type=staff&amp;p=189',0,'staff','',0),(191,1,'2015-03-23 13:01:40','2015-03-23 13:01:40','','Natalie KONDOR','','publish','closed','closed','','natalie-kondor','','','2015-03-23 13:01:40','2015-03-23 13:01:40','',0,'http://newthemes.themeple.co/vision_wp/?post_type=staff&amp;p=191',0,'staff','',0),(194,1,'2015-03-23 13:02:29','2015-03-23 13:02:29','','ALBERT BERENG','','publish','closed','closed','','albert-bereng','','','2015-03-23 13:02:29','2015-03-23 13:02:29','',0,'http://newthemes.themeple.co/vision_wp/?post_type=staff&am