-09-03 06:47:23','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"]\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">TAKING LOCAL INNOVATION GLOBAL</h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Finnish innovator in cattle-feed supplements sees global market benefits through a strategic partnership with Intellectual Ventures’ Invention Development Fund.</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"]\r\n[/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>NEW CATTLE FEED OFFERS WORLDWIDE BENEFITS</h2>\r\nRaisio, a leading European food production company, develops cattle-feed supplements that make milk production safer, more efficient, and more environmentally responsible. These innovative feeds, successfully launched to the Finnish Dairy industry as the Benemilk® product line, are now poised for international success through broader geographical licensing and IP augmentation.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yl9ocRrY4fo\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2977\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441134053801{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442859621077{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2>JOINT VENTURE AGREEMENT ENABLES GLOBAL REACH</h2>\r\nTo obtain the necessary expertise and global reach, Raisio is working with Intellectual Ventures, a recognized world leader in strengthening IP portfolios and marketing new innovations. In ongoing partnership, they will seek to leverage the value of Raisio’s core technology via Intellectual Ventures’ global network of inventors and world-class patent and licensing know-how. The April 2013 announcement of a joint venture between Raisio and Intellectual Ventures’ Invention Development Fund transfers ownership of the original invention to a new jointly owned Finnish company, Benemilk® Oy.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>ONGOING YIELDS, ONGOING INNOVATION</h2>\r\nThe agreement provides Raisio with continued success in Finland along with the added benefit of introducing their invention to dairy markets worldwide. And Intellectual Ventures is also helping with the discovery and application of complementary innovations to further promote safe, efficient, and environmentally responsible food production.\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2976\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“Our work with IDF and its international invention ecosystem brings the best possible expertise and resources to bear upon the improvement, patenting, enforcement, and global commercialization of our inventions.” </em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">— Raisio CEO Matti Rihko</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Raisio Benemilk','','publish','open','closed','','case-study-raisio-benemilk','','','2015-10-16 20:12:47','2015-10-16 20:12:47','',0,'http://inventiondevfund.com/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=2650',0,'portfolio','',0),(2651,1,'2015-09-03 06:48:21','2015-09-03 06:48:21','','home-thumb2','','inherit','open','closed','','home-thumb2','','','2015-09-03 06:48:21','2015-09-03 06:48:21','',2650,'http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/home-thumb2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2657,1,'2015-09-03 06:55:41','2015-09-03 06:55:41','','home-thumb3','','inherit','open','closed','','home-thumb3','','','2015-09-03 06:55:41','2015-09-03 06:55:41','',2296,'http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/home-thumb3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2668,1,'2015-09-03 07:13:06','2015-09-03 07:13:06','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1445026243276{margin-top: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">GAINING ACCESS TO INNOVATION</h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Global leader in paint and coatings teams up with Intellectual Ventures to explore potential for new product innovations.</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>VISIONARY ENTERPRISE</h2>\r\nNetherlands-based AkzoNobel, the world’s largest paint and coatings company, is a major producer of specialty chemicals with a passionate emphasis on developing and delivering sustainable solutions to their customers. In line with their guiding philosophy of Tomorrow’s Answers Today™, AkzoNobel continually seeks new technologies to provide improved products to industries and consumers worldwide.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3041\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2824\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441134053801{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442859976678{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2>COOPERATIVE INNOVATION</h2>\r\nIn pursuit of new paint and coating technologies, AkzoNobel has been working cooperatively with the Invention Development Fund at Intellectual Ventures (IV). Through a joint collaboration agreement, the companies will work with the IV Invention Network of more than 10,000 inventors, research institutions and universities, to discover and develop potential new products. The partnership also provides AkzoNobel access to existing technologies in the IV portfolio of chemistry and materials science inventions.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>COMMERCIAL POTENTIAL</h2>\r\nThe benefits of this agreement for AkzoNobel include the option to expand upon discoveries generated through this project, allowing for future product development and commercialization opportunities. The working relationship with Intellectual Ventures provides AkzoNobel the potential for new coating technologies that will improve its competitive position in the global marketplace.\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2827\" img_size=\"large\" alignment=\"right\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“This collaboration with Intellectual Ventures aims to enhance the innovation pipelines available to AkzoNobel to help us achieve our goal of continued improvement and new product introductions.” </em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>– </em>Jos Keurentjes, AkzoNobel Director of Open Innovation</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','AkzoNobel','','publish','closed','closed','','case-study-akzonobel','','','2015-10-16 20:11:14','2015-10-16 20:11:14','',0,'http://inventiondevfund.com/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=2668',0,'portfolio','',0),(2669,1,'2015-09-03 07:12:26','2015-09-03 07:12:26','','home-thumb3-freshblue','','inherit','open','closed','','home-thumb3-freshblue','','','2015-09-03 07:12:26','2015-09-03 07:12:26','',0,'http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/home-thumb3-freshblue.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2682,1,'2015-09-