ng. The other end of pedal arm is maintained free and the whole arm\r\n is adopted to slide in with in aguide/slotted bracket. This system\r\n almost double the torque of conventional pedal-crank generated by way\r\n of pedal-crank of the invention.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n Summary of Result\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n During the prior art search found the invention noteworthy, efficient\r\n application and cost effective and this leverage technology favor to\r\n all mechanical driven subjects\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n No highly relevant prior art encompassing all the features of the\r\n given invention such as was found.\r\n\r\n The search was focused on cycle rickshaw with the leverage system\r\n which aids the wheel to roll faster and easier, where in\r\n\r\n Leverage system with spinner moving through spinner rod\r\n\r\n Reduce pollution\r\n\r\n Increase speed\r\n\r\n Achieve longer distance in shorter timing\r\n\r\n Reduce pulling pressure.\r\n\r\n The following prior considered as noteworthy  reference and given under List B\r\n\r\n During course of search, one web reference relating to a cycle\r\n rickshaw was found and it is considered as interesting web reference\r\n and given under the title Non Patent Literature.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n A simple and cost effective manner of improving the torque generated\r\n through pedal-crank system which would favor drivers and efficient\r\n application of such as pedal-crank system  in variety of mechanical\r\n driven subjects.\r\n\r\n  I am quite content with this patent report and thanks to everyone\r\n worked for this Patent Report which favors  the need of the hour.\r\n Wheelchair can be driven with fingers control by pressing upward by\r\n connected bar in finger position. By single slow presser up word by\r\n fingers wheelchair start to roll about 350 feet distance it can be\r\n slower or faster. By suitable modification with sunshield it can be\r\n used for long distance travels.\r\n\r\n I wish to have your kind perusal although I am not sure who gets my\r\n letter and going through it. I hope and expect your kind review on my\r\n invention at the earliest.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n Thanks\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n With many regards\r\n\r\n Rugus\r\n\r\n Thanks\r\n\r\n With regards Rugus\r\n 919538598487\r\n Bangalore- 560043\r\n Apt, A- Block, G-2, MM Garden Road, Babusapalya, Bangalore- 560043'),(95,'Hay my name is Johnny walker  I am a inventor  the name of my invention is the automatic door opener for your home with a hand held remote  I have a provisional patent on my invention  I have a engineered drawing of my invention that shows functionality  I am in the process of introducing my invention to manufacturing corporations  I will need seed funding and venture capital  thank you'),(111,'Hay my name is johnny walker   Ii am a inventor  The name of my invention is the automatic door opener for your home with a hand held remote  I have a provisional patent on my invention  I have a engineered drawing of my invention  That shows functionality on cds  I am looking to license my invention  I am looking to partner with a corporation  I am looking for seed funding and venture capital  Thank you'),(121,'hello,\r\n\r\nI have been developing a design with an eye on obtaining a provisional patent for over 5 years.  I am at the point of building various scaled prototypes, for this invention can indeed be as big, and as small as necessary.  It fits within the alternative energy space and requires no fuel, or outside influence to start or maintain motion in generating electricity.  It will be the most amazing and thought provoking thing you will ever see, I am sure of it.  I took the idea from a under appreciated inventor from the 1700\'s during the time of Newtons fame.  He never obtained any buyers, or a patent, and eventually dismantled all his working prototypes leaving only notes and drawings behind.  Before passing away, he left instructions to all interested parties to utilize his notes and drawings, poems and diagrams for in them 