ity etc... , Sincerely yours, Stephanie M. Curtis.  My talent and knowledge come from my time and experiences from the French Dir Force of which I was a test flight technician.  To cut short this already elaborated  introduction, I have now a fairly new patent, WIND TURBINE GENERATOR SYSTEM, US 7 888 810 B2, based on the principle of the jet engine.  It\'s quite cool.\r\n\r\nYou all gentlemen  have an interesting and encouraging introduction-quote by D. Belliveau, which I trust, meaning that now I must and I do trust you with my WIND TURBINE GENERATOR\"  hoping that you could be my best in \"partnership\"  with the right intent to develop this \"SYSTEM.\"  when and if you are interesting to work with me/me, understandably, with you, we could help make our world a quantum leap towards positive results in counterbalancing (some of) the global warming.  The bridge between vision and illumination takes as little as a simple \"flick it.\"\r\n\r\nThank you so very much for  your professional attention to a much-French-talker who became a U.S. citizen by naturalization, in October 1974, in Danville, Ill., when I was professor technical director to Illinois Wesleyan U, and Columbia College (not University) in Chicago, Ill.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\n\r\nPaul Moretto (619)  262 4181'),(270,'To whom it may concern,\r\n\r\nHello! My name is Patrick A. Hillman, I am 23 years old and have recently separated from the US Air Force and have been working on ideas that some day I would like to invent. Recently one idea has stuck with me for some time and I would like to get some input and advice on how to go about possibly making it a reality. I prefer to be contacted by email as I am a car salesman and constantly busy or on the phone with customers. I have emailed other places asking the same question and no one has emailed me back, so when I receive an email back with some information or asking me for more information, that is when it will be provided. I greatly appreciate any information and your time.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nPatrick A Hillman'),(285,'Dear Sir/Madam,\r\nI would like to apply for partnership with IDF as I need to readily co-operate with you to help me finish the process of my invention and to be on the market.It has been a long time dream looking for support.\r\nLet me hear from you.\r\nYour faithfully,\r\nLameck Mbewe.\r\n(In Africa)'),(290,'Dear Sir/Madam,\r\nI would like to apply for partnership with IDF as I need to readily co-operate with you to help me finish the process of my invention and to be on the market.It has been a long time dream looking for support.\r\nLet me hear from you.\r\nYour faithfully,\r\nLameck Mbewe.\r\n(In Africa)');
